node.text:
The Dolce&Gabbana Alta Sartoria collection arouses unique emotions as exquisite silks, brocades, velvets, glass and crystals, embroideries and precious fabrics come together in a perfect melody of beauty and Italian craftsmanship. 

Watch the #DGAltaSartoria show and discover more at the link in bio. 
 
#DGLovesVenice #DGFattoAMano #MadeInItaly #DolceGabbana

Discover more exclusive content at the link in bio.
 
#DGFattoAMano #MadeInItaly

“Dolce&Gabbana is the ultimate expression of femininity. It represents everything great about Italy.” 
 
In a personal interview, @kitty.spencer reveals her favourite things about being an Ambassador for #DolceGabbana. 
 
Her looks include iconic black dresses paired with a black #DGGirlsBag, black sapphire and gold jewellery and a #DGDevotion necklace.

node.text:
Exploring our roots to create what's next: introducing #DGNextChapter, the Women's Fall Winter 21 Fashion Show.
 
In collaboration with @istitutoitalianoditecnologia, the #DGFW21 Collection reveals how technology and craftsmanship, two apparently different worlds, come together in a celebration of Fatto a Mano. The new looks, inspired by robotics research and Artificial Intelligence, also pay tribute to #DolceGabbana DNA of the ‘90s. 
 
Stay tuned for the Fashion Show on Monday, March 1st at 4PM CET.

Don’t miss #DGTogether presented exclusively with @farfetch, today at 3PM CET.

The magical city of Venice, captured through the lens of @branislavsimoncik represents the true essence of Italian beauty, through an astonishing tour around its so-called “Calli”, the typical Venetian streets, and its celebrated treasures.  
 
The #DGAltaModa look is composed of a hand-painted triple Mikado jacket with velvet detailing embroidered with Lurex brocade, Lurex lace, crystals and cabochons, and embellished with jewelled buttons, paired with Lurex brocade trousers. 
 
#DGLovesVenice #DGFattoAMano #MadeInItaly

node.text:
The magical city of Venice, captured through the lens of @branislavsimoncik represents the true essence of Italian beauty, through an astonishing tour around its so-called “Calli”, the typical Venetian streets, and its celebrated treasures.  
 
The #DGAltaModa look is composed of a double duchesse smoking jacket embroidered with macramé lace, Lurex thread and crystals, and embellished with a piping and Lurex fringe belt, paired with a silk satin shirt and a “Soprarizzo” velvet skirt. 
 
#DGLovesVenice #DGFattoAMano #MadeInItaly

node.text:
The magical city of Venice, captured through the lens of @branislavsimoncik represents the true essence of Italian beauty, through an astonishing tour around its so-called “Calli”, the typical Venetian streets, and its celebrated treasures.  
 
The #DGAltaModa look is composed of a printed duchesse and brocade kaftan embroidered with sequins, bugle beads and crystals paired with a silk tulle corset dress. 
 
#DGLovesVenice #DGFattoAMano #MadeInItaly
